#: ../../ai-agent/domain-routing.md:32
msgid "`hr.employee`, `hr.attendance`, `hr.payslip`, `hr.leave`, `hr.applicant`"
msgstr "`hr.employee`, `hr.attendance`, `hr.payslip`, `hr.leave`, `hr.applicant`"

#: ../../ai-agent/domain-routing.md:32
